We received the payment for your order!

<% if @order.shipments.empty? %>
    Congrats, we got the payment for your order and will soon ship it.
<% else %>
    Congrats, we got the payment for your order which also has been already shipped.
<% end %>

=== General information ===

Order: <%= '#' + @order.number %>
E-mail: <%= @order.customer.email %>
Order date: <%= I18n.l @order.placed_at, format: :long %>
Paid with: <%= @order.payment_means.type %>
Paid date: <%= I18n.l @order.payment_means.paid_at, format: :long %>

=== Billing addresss ===

<%= render partial: 'address', locals: { address: @order.billing_address } %>